Motormaster looks around, "Well Scourge, there is no sense in staying here.
Rip the blasters off of that shuttle" he tells him. He then receives the
message from Drag Strip, "Well, we're done here, head back to base, and if
you see any of the other Decepticons there, tell them to do the same".
